<div
    data-c-accordion
    data-c-background="white(100)"
    data-c-margin="bottom(normal)"
    data-c-border="top(thin, solid, black) right(thin, solid, black) left(thin, solid, black)">
    <button
        data-c-background="white(100)"
        aria-expanded="false"
        data-c-accordion-trigger
        data-c-padding="right(triple)"
        tabindex="0"
        type="button">
        <div data-c-padding="top(normal) right bottom(normal) left(normal)">
            <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-font-size="h5" data-c-margin="bottom(half)" data-c-colour="c2">Task 4</p>
            <p>
                Build a diverse pipeline of candidates and strong partnerships with government departments. This means proactively going out and building a network and strong relationships with senior level external talent (CIOs and similar senior-level positions) across Canada, as well as with senior leaders in departments and agencies who have vacant positions.
            </p>
            <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="top(half)" data-c-heading="h5">
                2 Skills Selected
            </p>
        </div>
        <span data-c-visibility="invisible">
            Click to view...
        </span>
        <i
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="fas fa-plus"
            data-c-accordion-add>
        </i>
        <i
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="fas fa-minus"
            data-c-accordion-remove>
        </i>
    </button>
    <div
        aria-hidden="true"
        data-c-accordion-content>
        <div>
            <div data-c-background="grey(10)" class="job-build-add-skill" data-c-padding="all(normal)">
                <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(3of6) ds(5of8)">
                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold">Add a New Skill</p>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <button data-c-dialog-id="example-dialog-01" data-c-dialog-action="open">
                            <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="job-builder-skill" data-c-padding="all(normal)">
                <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(3of6) ds(5of8)">
                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Networking Abilities</p>
                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Moderately in Evidence</p>
                        <p>Defined as: Familiarity with the Canadian digital and high-tech community leading to quality of being trusted and having “street credibility”. Preference given to those who already have an established network connected to IT executives and CIO communities in Canada.</p>
                        <div data-c-margin="top(normal)" data-c-tag="c1" data-c-font-size="small">Also selected in 1 other task (Task 3).</div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <button type="button">
                            <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <button type="button" class="delete">
                            <i data-c-colour="stop" class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="job-builder-skill" data-c-padding="all(normal)">
                <div data-c-grid="gutter middle">
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(3of6) ds(5of8)">
                        <p data-c-font-weight="bold" data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Social Media Savviness</p>
                        <p data-c-margin="bottom(half)">Required Level: Asset</p>
                        <p>Defined as: Ability to use social media platforms effectively to reach a desired target audience.</p>
                        <div data-c-margin="top(normal)" data-c-tag="c1" data-c-font-size="small">Also selected in 2 other tasks (Tasks 1, 6).</div>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <button type="button">
                            <i data-c-colour="c1" class="fas fa-edit"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                    <div data-c-align="centre" data-c-grid-item="base(1of1) tp(1of6) ds(1of8)">
                        <button type="button" class="delete">
                            <i data-c-colour="stop" class="fas fa-trash"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
